Package: hazrd
Title: Polygenic Hazard Score with Cox Proportional Hazards Model
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Andrew", 
           family = "Morris", 
           email = "andrewmorris@mailbox.org", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to evaluate and visualize Polygenic Hazard Score (PHS)
    analyses. Provides a consistent API for computing survival-based
    discrimination metrics (hazard ratio, C-index, odds ratio, HR per SD),
    bootstrapped confidence intervals, and Kaplan-Meier curves stratified by
    PHS percentile group.
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: 
    boot,
    dplyr,
    ggplot2 (>= 3.5.1),
    scales (>= 1.3.0),
    survival,
    tibble,
    utils
